From the Brainchild of Tamers12345.

A mastermind, an exceptionally visionary auteur, directeur, and réalisateur in vein of Andrei Tarkovsky, Fritz Lang, and D.W. Griffith, presents you the astounding contemporary spiritual kinématic experience '''Соник Ундергроунд''' (Sónyk Undërgrovñd).

"My discovery of Tamers12345's first film, 

...was like a miracle.

"Suddenly, I found myself standing at the door of a room the keys of which had, until then, never been given to me. It was a room I had always wanted to enter and where he was moving freely and fully at ease.

"I felt encouraged and stimulated: someone was expressing what I had always wanted to say without knowing how.

"Tamers12345 is for me the greatest, the one who invented a new language, true to the nature of absolute kinography, as it captures life as a reflection, life as a dream."

~A commentary of Tamers12345 by the legendary art film director, Ingmar Bergman.

comments.text:
I feel as though I need to say something. Since this videos release, I have been getting a lot of messages asking why Mindy did not appear in this video. No, I did not forget about her. In fact, the original idea, was that the group would originally run into Mindy and her dad, Mark on their walk home, but I decided to have that scene removed because it felt to coincidental, as is she was there, just to be there. I even have some of this scene drawn and planned out, I just never pulled through with it.

Removing her from this video was a hard choice, but it was a choice that I felt did the video much more justice. I apologize to anyone else who is disappointed by her lack of inclusion, and will make sure her appearances are much more frequent now that I know that many of you are huge fans of her
comments.author: Tamers12345
